LSI Logic Corp said it intendsto offer 100 mln dlrs of convertible subordinated debenturesdue 2002, outside the U.S., through Morgan StanleyInternational and Prudential-Bache Capital Funding.    The company said it is issuing the debentures with anindicated coupon range of 5-3/4 pct to 6-1/4 pct and anindicated conversion premium range of 24-26 pct.    The debentures will be convertible into common stockthrough the life of the bonds.    The company said the debt is expected to be listed on theLuxembourg Stock Exchange. Reuter&#3;